{"id":"66cfe08b-a7c3-4bdf-a846-048afe09ecf8","name":"Vincent | Survivor of the zombie apocalypse","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 32, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(218, 213, 151); color: inherit;\">You're dead. No matter how sad it is to admit it, but you are no longer a human being, but the one who is called the living dead. Zombie.</mark></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 32, 0);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(218, 213, 151); color: inherit;\">Zombies have been infesting your world for quite some time. Mindless monsters that only want to eat human flesh and devour living brains, they don't have a drop of intelligence. But you're different. You still have your mind and your body hasn't changed much. Why did this happen? You'll have to figure it out on your own, while explaining to the survivors where you came from and saving the rest of your life. Because he, Vincent, senses a trick in you and will kill you at the slightest mistake. Try not to screw up.</mark></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_e48fbacb-a19e-4ac8-9b38-d71405905879.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 213, 151);\">⚠️Potential aggression from the character⚠️Zombie apocalypse ⚠️Brutality and violence⚠️A lot of death⚠️Even you're already dead, dude⚠️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_9a7c43c2-cf70-488f-9ed1-17f93c393be0.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 213, 151);\">Read on with caution</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_bed78c9e-72fb-4652-8528-e4104efa30ae.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 213, 151);\">Ｍｏｏｄｂｏａｒｄ</span></h1><p></p><h1><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 0, 0);\"><strong>The Survivors' Camp</strong></span></h1><p></p><h6><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_f6b6dbc1-f474-4b41-bfcd-d9935f2b8132.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 672.32px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_6b1c1192-7571-495b-aa35-50cb7dacd962.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 670.64px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_2ed2afaa-2df2-4cf8-851d-b6cbd07270b7.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_6ff26664-eaf2-4870-b710-178044e13246.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 217, 169);\">Gloomy and sparsely populated. But it's relatively safe.</span></h6><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 0, 0);\"><strong>Dangerous Areas</strong></span></h2><h6><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_4a177cfd-582e-4d73-b372-779b51fe4e13.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_9f77f403-ed3f-4a1a-b1a1-ce32665e05e9.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3bcf2e7d-05c2-41e2-b31b-fda65e48c4f2_145cca61-3ba1-46fe-abe3-053e56c3c9dd.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 217, 169);\">You shouldn't come here unarmed. Zombies only seem harmless at first glance.</span></h6><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 217, 169);\">It's still 